title: Rhode Island College Claims GNAC Championship (Saint Joseph's College of Maine Athletics)
text: ( Source : Saint Joseph's College of Maine Athletics ) NORTH DARTMOUTH, Mass. - Rhode Island College shot a collective 635 to claim their fifth straight team title at the 2015 Great Northeast Athletic Conference ( GNAC ) Men's Golf Championship
